when you enter a temple.

759
01:08:46,085 --> 01:08:50,798
Vaisravana keeps yakshas
and rakshasas in check

760
01:08:51,424 --> 01:08:55,011
and protects Buddha's ways and all humans.

761
01:08:57,388 --> 01:08:59,473
